flowchart TD
    Start([Log In]) --> AutoRedirect[Auto-Redirected to Admin Dashboard]
    AutoRedirect --> Dashboard[Dashboard\nTotal Users · Shops · Orders · Revenue\nPending Approvals Alert]

    Dashboard --> ShopQueue{Pending Shop Approvals?}
    ShopQueue -- Yes --> ReviewShop[Review Shop Details]
    ReviewShop --> ShopDecision{Decision}
    ShopDecision -- Approve --> ShopLive[Shop Goes Live]
    ShopDecision -- Suspend --> ShopBlocked[Shop Blocked]
    ShopLive --> Users
    ShopBlocked --> Users
    ShopQueue -- No --> Users

    Users[User Management\nView All Buyers & Sellers] --> UserAction{Action Needed?}
    UserAction -- Suspend User --> Suspended[Account Suspended\nCannot Log In]
    UserAction -- Reinstate --> Active[Account Reinstated]
    UserAction -- Skip --> Products
    Suspended --> Products
    Active --> Products

    Products[Product Moderation\nSearch All Products] --> ProductAction{Action}
    ProductAction -- Deactivate --> Hidden[Product Hidden from Storefront]
    ProductAction -- Delete --> Removed[Product Permanently Removed]
    ProductAction -- Skip --> OrdersMgmt
    Hidden --> OrdersMgmt
    Removed --> OrdersMgmt

    OrdersMgmt[Order Management\nView All Orders by Status] --> OrderAction{Override Needed?}
    OrderAction -- Yes --> ForceStatus[Force Order to Any Status\ne.g. Cancelled or Delivered]
    OrderAction -- No --> Categories
    ForceStatus --> Categories

    Categories[Category Management] --> CatAction{Action}
    CatAction -- Add / Edit --> SaveCategory[Save Category\nSlug Auto-Generated]
    CatAction -- Reorder --> Reordered[Display Order Updated]
    CatAction -- Delete --> CheckProducts{Products in Category?}
    CheckProducts -- Yes --> WarnDelete[Warning: Products Become Uncategorized]
    CheckProducts -- No --> Deleted[Category Deleted]
    WarnDelete --> Deleted
    SaveCategory --> Financials
    Reordered --> Financials
    Deleted --> Financials

    Financials[Financials] --> FinAction{Task}
    FinAction -- View Log --> TxLog[Read-Only Transaction Log\nAll Orders · Gross Revenue · Status]
    FinAction -- Adjust Rate --> CommRate[Set Commission Percentage\nApplies to Future Payouts]
    FinAction -- Process Payout --> SelectShop[Select Shop with Unpaid Revenue]
    SelectShop --> Preview[Preview Payout\nGross minus Commission equals Net]
    Preview --> CreatePayout[Create Payout Record]
    CreatePayout --> MarkPaid[Mark as Paid + Log Transaction Ref]
    TxLog --> Support
    CommRate --> Support
    MarkPaid --> Support

    Support[Support Inbox\nTabbed by Status] --> TicketAction{Ticket Type}
    TicketAction -- General or Bug or Complaint --> ReplyThread[Reply in Conversation Thread]
    TicketAction -- Order Dispute --> QuickAction[Use Quick Action Panel\nOverride Linked Order Status]
    ReplyThread --> UpdateStatus[Update Ticket Status\nIn Progress → Resolved → Closed]
    QuickAction --> UpdateStatus
    UpdateStatus --> Dashboard
